{
  "texts": [
    "Assembly jobs enter the assembly system in a predefined order, considering a restricted number of work in progress (WIP).",
    "Whenever a job gets finished (all assembly operations of the job are finished), a new job enters the system.",
    "Each job belongs to a specific product type.",
    "Several product types are defined a priori.",
    "When a new job is created, a product type is assigned based on an equal probability distribution of all possible product types."
  ]
}